🌞New challenge announcement🌞

open to all levels🌸🌸🌸
There is always a first time, isn’t it? 
Come begin your YOGA journey with us! Now is the time and what better way than to just START. 😀
If you are already practicing, you can join us to strengthen your practice through this challenge and spread your inspiration to all the newcomers. 👍👍

Here’s what the challenge is all about..🤩🌝
Get yourself ready for Surya Namaskaras with us. Grab your mat and let’s do yoga 🌞🧘🏻‍♀️🤸‍♂️

#starttheyoga
📌Date : 7 - 12 September 

