🌈🌈 Day wise detail of the challenge 🌈🌈

☀️Day 1 : talk about your yoga journey or why you want to start and start with a bang with any back bend / hastauttanasana / ardha kati chakrasana 
☀️Day 2 : any forward fold / uttanasana
☀️Day 3 : any pose for spine /ashwa sanchalana / runner's pose / stretch with the knee bent 
☀️Day 4 : arm balance / plank / phalakasana
☀️Day 5 :  inversion / downdog / sarvangasana / head down pose 
☀️Day 6 : surya namaskar (any) of your choice

How to participate📝
⚡1. Follow all hosts and sponsors .
⚡2. Help us spread the word by reposting this flyer and tag at least 5 friends to join you!
⚡3. Post a picture each day using the hashtag #starttheyoga and tag all hosts & sponsors.
⚡4. Ensure your profile is public & you have your country in your profile.
⚡5. Have fun and spread some love to your fellow hosts, sponsors and participants during the challenge.

